            <div type="a">
                <column>5</column>
                <head>More Amalgamation</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>A negro at Hartford, Pennsylvania, named John Sophia, recently ran away with 
                        a white girl name Amelia Pinley, eighteen years of age, and married her.  The girl belongs to a 
                        respectable family, and the elopement and marriage were brought about by an Abolitionist named 
                        Whiting, and his wife.</p>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
